definitions.definition: The process or result of something being spouted ; that which is spouted.
examples: Spoutings of lava shot from the crest of the volcano.
The spoutings of a large whale can be seen from a great distance.

definitions.definition: A gutter under the eaves of a building; guttering .
examples: The spouting was filled with leaves and needed cleaning.
